## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="4092c-160"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> не следует вызывать до окончания загрузки документа, который его реализует.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-160"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4092c-161">Можно обнаружить при завершении загрузки документа путем обработки <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> событий.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-161">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="4092c-162">Приведенный ниже показано, как вызвать функцию скрипта в документе из [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] приложений с помощью <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-162">The following example shows how to call a script function in a document from a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4092c-163">В этом примере функция скрипта не имеет параметров.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-163">In this example, the script function has no parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4092c-164">Ниже приведен [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] документ, который реализует функцию скрипта, которая будет вызываться из [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-164">The following is the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document that implements the script function that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function called!";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4092c-165">Ниже [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] реализацию для вызова функции сценария [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] документа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-165">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script function in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters");  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="4092c-173"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> не следует вызывать до окончания загрузки документа, который его реализует.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-173"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4092c-174">Можно обнаружить при завершении загрузки документа путем обработки <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> событий.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-174">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4092c-175">Если вы не передаете недостаточно значений параметров для сценария, который был вызван, параметры, которые вы не передаете значения будут иметь неопределенное значение.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-175">If you do not pass enough parameter values to the script that you are invoking, the parameters that you do not pass values to will have the undefined value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4092c-176">Если передать слишком много значений параметров, лишние значения игнорируются.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-176">If you pass too many parameter values, the excess values are ignored.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="4092c-177">Приведенный ниже показано, как вызов функции сценария в документе из приложения с помощью <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-177">The following example shows how to call script functions in a document from an application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4092c-178">В этом примере функции сценариев требуют параметров.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-178">In this example, the script functions require parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4092c-179">Ниже приведен документ, который реализует функции скриптов, которые будут вызываться из [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-179">The following is the document that implements the script functions that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function 'called: " + message + ".";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4092c-180">Ниже [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] реализацию для вызова скрипта функции в [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] документа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-180">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script functions in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters", this.messageTextBox.Text);  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="4092c-194">Вызов <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> имеет тот же эффект, что параметр <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> свойство.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-194">Calling <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> has the same effect as setting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4092c-195"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> используется из разметки разработчиков, желающих для декларативного указания начального документа, который <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> переходит к когда <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> инициализируется.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-195"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> is used from markup by developers who want to declaratively specify the initial document that <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to when <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is initialized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4092c-196">Используйте <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> метод для перехода к URL-адрес, который может содержать escape-символы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-196">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4092c-197">Используйте <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> метод для перехода к <xref:System.Uri> , которая не включает escape-символы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-197">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="4092c-198">В следующем примере показано, как использовать <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> для перехода к документу с помощью <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> метод.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4092c-198">The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> to navigate to a document by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute eg 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri);  
}  
```

  
  
